<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=The_Reason_(Hoobastank_song)&action=edit&section=6.php.html" title="Edit section: Covers">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Covers">Covers</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>In 2004 <a href="CKBE-FM" title="CKBE-FM">CKBE-FM</a> <a href="David_Tyler" title="David Tyler">David Tyler</a></li>
<li>The Irish pop band <a href="Westlife" title="Westlife">Westlife</a> recorded and included a cover on their eleventh album <i><a href="Gravity_(Westlife_album)" title="Gravity (Westlife album)">Gravity</a></i>.</li>
<li><i>The Reason</i> was covered by <a href="Tom_Jones_(singer)" title="Tom Jones (singer)">Tom Jones</a> in <a href="../../w/index-title=XLVIII_Festival_Internacional_de_la_Canci%C3%B3n_de_Vi%C3%B1a_del_Mar&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="XLVIII Festival Internacional de la Canción de Viña del Mar (page does not exist)">XLVIII Festival Internacional de la Canción de Viña del Mar</a> February 22, 2007.</li>
<li>British band The Reason4 have recorded the song for their debut album set for a 2011 release.</li>
<li><i>The Reason</i> was covered by <a href="Heather_Headley" title="Heather Headley">Heather Headley</a> in her 2012 album <i><a href="Only_One_in_the_World" title="Only One in the World">Only One in the World</a></i>.</li>
</ul>
